'''菲萊登陸器'''（Philae）是[[歐洲太空總署|歐洲太空總署]][[组织_(社会学)|組織]]的[[太空探測器|太空探測器]]計劃[[羅塞塔號|羅塞塔號]]所攜帶的一個[[機器人|機器人]]，随羅塞塔號一同前往[[67P/楚留莫夫－格拉希門克彗星|67P/楚留莫夫－格拉希門克彗星]]<ref name = UlamecActa>{{cite journal
| author = S. Ulamec, S. Espinasse, B. Feuerbacher, M. Hilchenbach, D. Moura, H. Rosenbauer, H. Scheuerle, R. Willnecker
| title = Rosetta Lander—Philae: Implications of an alternative mission
| journal = Acta Astronautica
| year=2006
| volume=58
| issue = 8
| pages =435–441
|doi = 10.1016/j.actaastro.2005.12.009 |bibcode = 2006AcAau..58..435U }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal
| author = J. Biele
| title = The Experiments Onboard the ROSETTA Lander
| journal = Journal Earth, Moon, and Planets
| year = 2002
| volume = 90
| issue = 1–4
| pages = 445–458
| doi = 10.1023/A:1021523227314 |bibcode = 2002EM&P...90..445B }}</ref><ref name="NASA-201401017">{{cite web |last1=Agle |first1=DC |last2=Cook |first2=Jia-Rui |last3=Brown |first3=Dwayne |last4=Bauer |first4=Markus |title=NASA Release = 2014-015 - Rosetta: To Chase a Comet |url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-015 |date=17 January 2014 |work=[[NASA|NASA]] |accessdate=18 January 2014 |archive-date=2016-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113181033/http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-015 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，并于2014年11月12日在彗星上着陆，成为有史以來第一個在彗星上的成功登陸的探測器<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/science/2014/11/141112_rosetta_landed_latest |title=BBC中文網：歐洲探測器完成人類史上首次登陸彗星行動 |accessdate=2014-11-12 |archive-date=2014-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113033934/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/science/2014/11/141112_rosetta_landed_latest |dead-url=no }}</ref>。登陸器上的儀器將獲得彗星第一手資訊，並率先分析其結構<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Europe_s_comet_chaser/ |title=Europe's Comet Chaser - Historic mission |publisher=European Space Agency |date=16 January 2014 |accessdate=5 August 2014 |archive-date=2014-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808213100/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Europe_s_comet_chaser/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。菲萊登陸器是由位于德国[[达姆施塔特|达姆施塔特]]的[[欧洲太空控制中心|欧洲太空控制中心]]（ESOC）追踪和控制。<ref>[http://www.esa.int/About_Us/ESOC ESOC at ESA website] {{Wayback|url=http://www.esa.int/About_Us/ESOC |date=20141115144923 }}, retrieved 13 November 2014.</ref>

菲萊登陸器是根據[[尼羅河|尼羅河]]上的[[菲萊_(埃及)|菲萊]]來命名，[[羅塞塔石碑|羅塞塔石碑]]在此出土。羅塞塔石碑破譯古埃及象形文字（[[聖書體|聖書體]]）。

== 任务 ==
菲莱的任务是成功登陆彗星表面上，附着在彗星上，以及把彗星的组成成分的数据从表面发送出来。一枚运载[[罗塞塔号|罗塞塔号]]太空船和菲莱登陆器的亞利安5G+火箭于2004年3月2日07:17 UTC从[[法属圭亚那|法属圭亚那]]发射，并且在旅行了3907天（10.7年）之后到达[[楚留莫夫－格拉希门克彗星|楚留莫夫－格拉希门克彗星]]。

=== 登陆 ===
在与[[67P/楚留莫夫－格拉希門克彗星|67P/楚留莫夫－格拉希門克彗星]]会合之后，菲莱登陆器仍然附着在罗塞塔号太空船上，直到2014年11月12日。在2014年9月15日，歐洲太空總署公布位于彗星小瓣上的“地点J”作为登陆的目的地。<ref name="esa20140915">{{cite news |url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/J_marks_the_spot_for_Rosetta_s_lander |title='J' Marks the Spot for Rosetta's Lander |publisher=European Space Agency |first=Markus |last=Bauer |date=15 September 2014 |accessdate=20 September 2014 |archive-date=2019-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419085938/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/J_marks_the_spot_for_Rosetta_s_lander |dead-url=no }}</ref>在歐洲太空總署十月的命名公众比赛之后，“J地点”更名为''Agilkia''以纪念{{le|Agilkia岛|Agilkia Island}}。<ref name="space20141105">{{cite news |url=http://www.space.com/27662-rosetta-comet-landing-site-agilkia.html |title=Historic Comet Landing Site Has a New Name: Agilkia |work=Space.com |first=Miriam |last=Kramer |date=5 November 2014 |accessdate=5 November 2014 |archive-date=2014-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108014232/http://www.space.com/27662-rosetta-comet-landing-site-agilkia.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2014年11月11日至12日进行一系列的四个“去/不去”检查。一次来自罗塞塔号分离前的最后测试的结果表明，着陆器的气体推进器没有正常的工作，但是“去”反正是决定的，因为它不可能被修复。<ref name=CS1>{{cite news |title=Will Philae successfully land on comet? Thruster trouble heightens drama. |author= |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/Science/2014/1112/Will-Philae-successfully-land-on-comet-Thruster-trouble-heightens-drama |newspaper=Christian Science Monitor |work= |date=12 November 2014 |accessdate=2014-11-17 |archive-date=2014-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141116184620/http://www.csmonitor.com/Science/2014/1112/Will-Philae-successfully-land-on-comet-Thruster-trouble-heightens-drama |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Rosetta and Philae go for separation|work=Rosetta Blog (ESA)|date=12 November 2014|url=http://blogs.esa.int/rosetta/2014/11/12/rosetta-and-philae-go-for-separation/|accessdate=2014-11-17|archive-date=2014-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112091304/http://blogs.esa.int/rosetta/2014/11/12/rosetta-and-philae-go-for-separation/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>菲莱登陆器于2014年11月12日08:35时（UTC）从罗塞塔号脱离，7小时后在15:35登陆。<ref name="esa20140926">{{cite news |url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Rosetta_to_deploy_lander_on_12_November |title=Rosetta to Deploy Lander on 12 November |publisher=European Space Agency |date=26 September 2014 |accessdate=4 October 2014 |archive-date=2014-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141113150506/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Space_Science/Rosetta/Rosetta_to_deploy_lander_on_12_November |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NASA-20141106-JP">{{cite news |url=http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-383 |title=Rosetta Races Toward Comet Touchdown |publisher=NASA |first=Jane |last=Platt |date=6 November 2014 |accessdate=7 November 2014 |archive-date=2014-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141119043808/http://www.jpl.nasa.gov/news/news.php?release=2014-383 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>一个确认登陆的訊号被在地球通信站在16:03 UTC接收到，- 有28[[光秒|光分钟]]的路程。<ref name=nssdc /><ref>{{cite web|title=Probe makes historic comet landing|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-30026398|website=BBC News|accessdate=12 November 2014|archive-date=2014-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141117035319/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-30026398|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===未來重啟===
菲萊登陸器因為電力不足而失去所有的通訊聯繫。但當彗星靠近太陽的時候，登陸器的太陽能板可以接受足夠的太陽能以重啟菲萊。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/results-comet-landers-experiments-expected-072322857.html|title=Scientists 'confident' comet lander will wake up|accessdate=November 18, 2014|publisher=Yahoo News|archive-date=2014-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141119232352/http://news.yahoo.com/results-comet-landers-experiments-expected-072322857.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===乍然甦醒===
2015年6月13日晚，[[羅塞塔號|羅塞塔號]]太空船收到從菲萊登陸器傳送的85秒訊息，表示登陸器已充電飽足，不再需要以[[安全模式|安全模式]]操作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.esa.int/rosetta/2015/06/14/rosettas-lander-philae-wakes-up-from-hibernation/|title=Rosetta's lander Philae wakes up from hibernation|publisher=European Space Agency, Rosetta Blog|date=14 June 2015|accessdate=14 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150614125638/http://blogs.esa.int/rosetta/2015/06/14/rosettas-lander-philae-wakes-up-from-hibernation/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。現儲存的24瓦特電力，登陸器準備診斷工作與重新運作。[[歐洲太空總署|歐洲太空總署]]報告，從菲萊傳送的歷史數據顯示，雖然它在13日前就已在工作，但它那時並未與羅塞塔號聯絡。<ref name="NAT-20150614">{{cite journal |last1=Biever |first1=Celeste |last2=Gibney |first2=Elizabeth |title=Philae comet lander wakes up and phones home |url=http://www.nature.com/news/philae-comet-lander-wakes-up-and-phones-home-1.17756 |date=14 June 2015 |journal=[[Nature_(journal)|Nature (journal)]] |doi=10.1038/nature.2015.17756 |accessdate=14 June 2015 |archive-date=2019-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190621124854/http://www.nature.com/news/philae-comet-lander-wakes-up-and-phones-home-1.17756 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===着陆点发现===
在上次重新恢复联系后，菲萊登陸器依然为失去联系，直到2016年9月5日，欧空局发布消息，说从羅塞塔號于9月2日用高分辨率相机拍摄到菲萊登陸器被卡在一条黑暗裂缝中，自此确认到精确的着陆位置和与羅塞塔號通信一直困难重重的原因。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tech.qq.com/a/20160906/007607.htm|title=罗塞塔号找到“菲莱”了！是“菲莱”不是“韭菜”哦_科技_腾讯网|accessdate=2016-09-06|archive-date=2016-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160906082657/http://tech.qq.com/a/20160906/007607.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

